The paper deals with the problem of tensor estimation and mutual information, which are topics related to information theory (cs.IT) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of interpolation methods and recursive techniques suggests a connection to numerical analysis (cs.NA) and data structures (cs.DS). The concept of layered structure may also relate to the field of signal processing (cs.SI).
